      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "IN MODERATION (8) was out of character last run when missing the frame, finishing fourth (34.82) in a Grade 4/5 at Sandown. Generally fast into stride but was shuffled back from the tricky draw last time. Has a strong record from box 8, including two wins. Can make amends. MIDNIGHT PHANTOM (1) is a capable type and proved too classy last time to win by 4.5 lengths at Shepparton in a handy 37.15 beating Joni Black. Is yet to miss the placings from this draw, including two wins, from seven starts. Will go close again if runs up to latest. ROMANTIC RED (5) doesn't win out of turn. Finished in the money last time though when second (43.78) at The Meadows. Has never missed the frame here at the trip from four starts. Didn't win last time but still ran one of the quickest times on the card. Winning chance. LADY NESS (4) can find the frame without surprising.",
